-- Akbank Hires Goldman to Advise on Stake Sale by Citigroup
-- B y   B e n j a m i n   H a r v e y
-- 2012-04-09T17:57:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-09/akbank-hires-goldman-to-advise-on-stake-sale-by-citigroup.html
Akbank TAS (AKBNK) , the Turkish bank in
which  Citigroup Inc. (C)  is planning to reduce its stake to less
than 10 percent from 20 percent, hired Goldman Sachs
International to advise it on the transaction.  Goldman will provide consultation to Akbank “in evaluating
various strategic options with regard to the Citigroup stake
sale,” Akbank said in a statement to the  Istanbul Stock
Exchange  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Benjamin Harvey in Istanbul at 
 bharvey11@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
